12.plot: Culinary dating series. Lucy from Surrey must choose three out of five men to dine with, based on the menus they have submitted. But when the dinners have been eaten and the dates are done, who will she want to see for seconds?

13.title: Episode #6.13
13.plot: Culinary dating series. This time, Luke from Southampton chooses dates from five menus. The ladies behind the three most appetising menus will each get the chance to entertain Luke at home, but he can only take one of them out for a second date. When the week is over and the meals are done and dusted, who will Luke want to see again?

14.title: Episode #6.14
14.plot: Another celebrity edition of the culinary dating show. Former Emmerdale star Gemma Oaten is given five menus, each put together by a potential blind date. The five men behind the menus have each come up with a three course meal, but Gemma will only be having dinner with three of them, choosing her dates based on the menus she most likes the look of. The three lucky guys have no idea that they will be opening the door to a celebrity, but when the dinners have been eaten and the dates are done, who will Gemma want to see for seconds?

15.title: Episode #6.15
15.plot: Dating series. Tony from Leeds chooses three blind dates from a pool of five women based on the menus they have prepared. Who will he choose to have seconds with?

16.title: Episode #6.16
16.plot: Culinary-themed dating series. This time, Drue from Bristol chooses three women to date based on the menus they have put together. After the dates are done and dusted, he can only choose to see one of them again, but who will it be?

17.title: Episode #6.17
17.plot: Dating series with an emphasis on food. Tatiana from Kent chooses three men to dine with from a possible five who have submitted menus. But when she has been wined and dined by the chosen three, who will she bring back to the table for seconds?

18.title: Episode #6.18
18.plot: Culinary dating series. This time, Robyn from Glasgow chooses three dates from five menus. The three men behind Robyn's chosen meals will each get the chance to entertain her, but she can choose only one chap to join her on another date. Which lucky guy will join her for seconds?

19.title: Episode #6.19
19.plot: Culinary-themed dating series. This time, Steph from Manchester chooses three dates based on the menus they have put together. After the dates are done and dusted, she can only choose to see one of them again, but who will it be?

20.title: Episode #6.20
20.plot: Dating series with a twist. Will Veronica from London find true love over the dining table? She chooses three men to dine with from five submitted menus - but who will she ask back for seconds?

21.title: Episode #6.21
21.plot: Culinary dating show. This time, Calvin from Greater Manchester chooses three women to date based on their temptingly tasty menus. After the three dates are done, Calvin will take his favourite chef and potential future beau out to a swanky restaurant, leaving the other two ladies with a night in alone with a ready meal for one. As they head out on their second date, will Calvin and his chosen lady find lasting love?
